---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Veritio - Evidence Graph for Software Systems"
  description="Open-source evidence protocol and hosted evidence vault for audit trails, AI change provenance, and governance workflows."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <nav>
        <strong>Veritio</strong>
        <div>
          <a href="#oss">OSS</a>
          <a href="#cloud">Cloud</a>
          <a href="#workbench">Workbench</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Open-source protocol. Managed evidence vault.</p>
        <h1>Evidence graph for audit trails, AI changes, and governance workflows.</h1>
        <p>
          Veritio helps teams record, connect, verify, and export application
          events, code changes, agent sessions, deployments, consent history,
          data subject workflows, and retention decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band" id="oss">
      <h2>OSS SDK</h2>
      <p>
        The public SDK and protocol stay useful without a hosted account:
        schemas, SDKs, storage adapters, self-hosted server, local Workbench,
        MCP server, verifier, and export bundle format.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="band" id="cloud">
      <h2>SaaS and PaaS</h2>
      <p>
        Hosted Veritio adds managed ingest, scoped keys, graph projection,
        customer portals, policy drift jobs, long retention, exports, regional
        storage controls, and operational service commitments.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="band" id="workbench">
      <h2>Local Workbench</h2>
      <p>
        Run <code>veritio dev --mcp</code> to test integrations locally with a
        visual evidence graph, verifier, scenario runner, and MCP tools for AI
        agents.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 76vh;
    padding: 24px clamp(20px, 5vw, 72px) 56px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgb(248 250 247 / 86%), rgb(248 250 247 / 96%)),
      url('/evidence-grid.svg');
    background-size: cover;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  nav div {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #44524a;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 960px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #4b6658;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 92px);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .hero-copy > p:last-child {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #38443d;
  }

  .band {
    padding: 56px clamp(20px, 5vw, 72px);
    border-top: 1px solid #dfe7df;
  }

  .band h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 28px;
  }

  .band p {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
    color: #3d4942;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  code {
    background: #e9efe8;
    border: 1px solid #d8e2d8;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 2px 6px;
  }
</style>
